From: Lucas <user@domain>
Subject: qml-asteroid: Include headers in -dev package

The asteroidapp.h header is installed by qml-asteroid but wasn't being
packaged in the -dev package, causing compilation failures in apps that
depend on it.

Upstream-Status: Pending

--- a/recipes-asteroid/qml-asteroid/qml-asteroid_git.bb
+++ b/recipes-asteroid/qml-asteroid/qml-asteroid_git.bb
@@ -15,4 +15,4 @@

 FILES:${PN} += "/usr/lib /usr/share/icons/asteroid/"
 FILES:${PN}-dbg += "/usr/lib/qml/org/asteroid/controls/.debug/ /usr/lib/qml/QtQuick/Controls/Styles/Asteroid/.debug/"
-FILES:${PN}-dev += "/usr/lib/mkspecs/ /usr/share/asteroidapp/cmake/ /usr/bin/asteroid-generate-desktop"
+FILES:${PN}-dev += "/usr/lib/mkspecs/ /usr/share/asteroidapp/cmake/ /usr/bin/asteroid-generate-desktop /usr/include/"
